    <summary>Tokio multiplexes thousands of I/O connections on a small thread pool. CPU-bound work must use spawn_blocking; independent calls use try_join!; every spawn handle must be awaited or dropped.</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>tokio</tag>
      <tag>async</tag>
      <tag>rust</tag>
